questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I make changes to the design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: : Definitely! The Fiver package includes three rounds of revisions to ensure your website is perfect.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is my website search engine friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I'll optimize your site for search engines, helping your art get discovered by a broader audience.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you design a website for my specific industry?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can design a website for any industry. I will work with you to understand your industry and target audience to create a custom design that meets your needs

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you ensure that the website is mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I design all websites with a mobile-first approach, which means that your website will be optimized for mobile devices. I also test all websites on different devices and screen sizes to ensure that they are responsive and user-friendly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you create a website from scratch, or do I need to provide you with a design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can create a website from scratch based on your requirements and preferences. However, if you already have a design or mockup, I can work with that too.
